Gifts to the capital
'Highwaymen' are ready to welcome new people into their camp, but first you have to earn it - by robbing a caravan of gifts to the capital.
#subobj 1
Come to the stopping place of the caravan
The caravan to the capital stopped briefly at the Karansula Property, where people who buy furs and game usually stop.
#subobj 2
Dealt with the ambush
There are armed people hiding nearby - so someone else has taken an interest in this caravan! You need to destroy the ambush without attracting the attention of the caravan security.
#subobj 3
Steal the gifts
The most valuable gifts to the capital lie in a chest on one of the carts.